    public class SetTag
extends CollectionTag

    A specialized CollectionTag implementation for creating sets.

    This tag handler class is very similar to ListTag, but it allows the creation of a java.util.Set object rather than a list. The tag can be placed in the body of a tag derived from {@link DependencyTag and sets the value of its parent tag to the newly created set. Alternatively the {
